- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as ASA is a type of optimization algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as ASA can be used in various AI applications such as optimization, machine learning, and robotics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as ASA can be used in optimization problems related to machine learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as ASA can be used in control systems optimization.
